 collapse threshold, given that AC also found that {\\em all} static\nsolutions are one-parameter unstable and sit on the threshold of collapse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2016 18:05:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2016 11:35:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-04"}
