H mass estimates for the\nmajority of high-luminosity, high-redshift, spectroscopically confirmed quasars\nin the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2016 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2017 10:17:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-23"}
