ly constant behaviour at 1<z<2.5. Our models indicate a steep decrease of\nthe global DTS at early times, which implies an expected decrease of the DTS at\nlarger redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2016 20:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-07"}
