al\ncharacteristics of the two solutions are discussed. These include the amplitude\namplification factor, the spatial evolution of complex-valued envelopes, their\ncorresponding physical wave fields and the evolution of the corresponding wave\nsignals. Interestingly, wavefront dislocation and phase singularity are\nobserved in both families of the solution with different patterns, depending on\nthe value of the modulation wavelength and on the choice of parameters in\nSFB$_{2}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 02:37:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-31"}
