ions and numerical models suggests that\nindeed acoustic waves (with a sound travel time of 68 s) could play an\nimportant role in redistributing energy and sustaining the enthalpy-based\nradiative cooling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 15:05:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
