nd provide a new direct\nproof of Sudakov Minoration via The Program.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 15:58:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 May 2018 12:26:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-08"}
